/>

## What’s Next

The machine works well, but there’s still a lot I want to explore. I’m thinking about upgrading the pen lifter for better control and less noise, experimenting with automatic pen switching, and improving the way I prepare and optimize drawings. I’m also curious about using real-world data to drive the art, or even training an AI agent to generate new visual styles.

If you’re curious, you can check out [sketches.aublet.ca](https://sketches.aublet.ca) — a small online gallery and sandbox for the project.
